<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然房間的打掃<delay20 />
完全沒做好<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但反正這是夢境，<delay8 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就算了吧～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">大家常說<delay20 /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的房間能讓人感到放鬆喔～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的房間怎麼樣呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呼哈<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="50" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你也想睡覺的話，<delay20 />隨意地找地方
躺下來睡覺也OK喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歡迎來到我的房間！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我想招待你吃點心，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是我剛剛不小心全吃完了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然進行大冒險的夢境也不錯，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但像這樣在家裡悠哉度過的夢境<delay8 />
也很棒！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果在夢境裡睡著的話，<delay20 />
醒來時可能會分不清楚<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是現實還是夢境的延續呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
